I told her vaya con Dios

39:44.299 --> 39:45.799
and I gave her 20 bucks.

39:47.052 --> 39:49.720
What was I supposed to say?

39:53.558 --> 39:55.609
Well, I'm sure we can get a replacement.

39:57.479 --> 39:59.897
We never needed a maid in Princeton.

40:09.207 --> 40:11.458
He wanted to kidnap the princess.

40:11.493 --> 40:13.827
So Zeus disguised himself

40:13.878 --> 40:15.996
as a giant white bull, Taurus,

40:15.998 --> 40:19.716
and he carried her on his
back across the ocean to Crete

40:19.751 --> 40:22.336
where he raped her, basically.

40:22.338 --> 40:25.055
And she never saw her family again.

40:28.259 --> 40:30.344
How do you know so much?

40:30.346 --> 40:33.680
We had a telescope in Princeton.

40:35.350 --> 40:38.102
Where is that?

40:38.153 --> 40:40.404
It's where I'm from.

40:40.438 --> 40:43.190
Where I'm going back to.

40:46.077 --> 40:48.078
Not too soon, I hope.

41:12.887 --> 41:14.771
Thanks for the ride.

41:14.806 --> 41:17.391
Sure.

41:20.895 --> 41:22.696
So, what happens now?

41:24.449 --> 41:27.234
We go back to being sworn enemies?

41:34.742 --> 41:36.460
Hair of the dog?

41:36.494 --> 41:39.079
I got two bottles of whiskey

41:39.130 --> 41:41.331
burning a hole in my suitcase.

41:48.256 --> 41:50.140
No.

41:50.175 --> 41:51.458
Thank you.

41:54.462 --> 41:56.930
- See you around.
- Yeah.

42:16.618 --> 42:19.002
Well, well, well.

42:19.037 --> 42:20.787
I'd give you a hero's welcome,

42:20.789 --> 42:23.957
but as you can see, I have my hands full
with this pile of work you left behind.

42:23.959 --> 42:26.093
Is Frank here?

42:27.128 --> 42:28.378
Hardly.

42:28.380 --> 42:30.380
No. No, it's just me.

42:55.373 --> 42:58.242
As long as we're both
stranded here in the desert,

42:58.293 --> 43:00.327
how about a drop to drink?

43:11.339 --> 43:14.258
Or we could skip the drink.

43:31.276 --> 43:34.828
Hi.

43:34.862 --> 43:38.749
How was wherever you were?

43:41.119 --> 43:42.669
Not home.

43:52.548 --> 43:55.215
I love you, Abby.

44:03.775 --> 44:08.862
Oh, wow.

44:15.453 --> 44:18.121
I have to go back to the office.

44:20.708 --> 44:24.578
Now? What's wrong?

44:27.915 --> 44:29.750
I don't know yet.

